波佢都照谷上2500-3000"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T07:41:19.000Z","msg":"我唔肯定你架車有冇問題<br />\n但2000到3000呢個區間係一般車最好既上波(升檔)區間"},{"pid":"8a978b942aec7a5b1516d210301968ea5bc36bea","tid":868970,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T11:29:21.000Z","msg":"唔通下下二千轉就轉波咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691f72344b6aa5b0e74c4737a0744e30e4757f4b","tid":868970,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:14:27.000Z","msg":"係咪你自己揸得好熱血咋"},{"pid":"28a4d72f99976275b7da61914e85bec146700bc0","tid":868970,"uid":183798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"691f72344b6aa5b0e74c4737a0744e30e4757f4b","tid":868970,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:14:27.000Z","msg":"係咪你自己揸得好熱血咋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話唔定係"},{"pid":"a6e5e6fa044fdebdb7d7c3e65b818107c1685b2e","tid":868970,"uid":87555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"二千幾轉有乜咁出奇..<br />\n<br />\n仲有可能就係電腦detect到冇力咪唔轉波住<br />\n例如我試過死咗一個氣缸 架車死都唔轉波因為電腦知部車冇力<br />\n好多原因但係二千幾轉我真係覺得唔洗check咁多.. check又要洗錢又煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a571a46cdbb9bee870f94ac737ccd2b89f6837","tid":868970,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T08:22:49.000Z","msg":"三千五轉都唔轉波先擔心啦"},{"pid":"0f88b6f2780b04a35e5c4df82ed7f74d42779e82","tid":868970,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T08:25:32.000Z","msg":"其實樓主明唔明<br />\n如果一到二千轉就轉波，上到去可能得千二三轉<br />\n乜柒力都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe156d3a6a5fd8a653cb188ba549c5e73464636","tid":868970,"uid":183798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T08:36:45.000Z","msg":"明 但係之前架車無咁嘈 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩個月前換左機油<br />\n<br />\n換之前就好似依家咁 一踩就好嘈 1500-2000已經好嘈 換左之後無事左兩個月 依家又開始番 <br />\n<br />\n個師傅話舊車漏油 但話大約半年至一年加番啲油就無事 因為整黎都曬氣 呢面封左 戈面就漏 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主要係因為嘈左 覺得古怪"}]}